  "description": [
    "ALIENS SMUGGLED INTO US BY PLANE Detroit Is Called Weak Spot in Frontier Wall Erected by Congress _Wlth 1300000 aliens illegally in tha United Stales the small border patrol light a losing battle with international muggier ring Thia la article 11 of a aerie revealing the schemes of the bor derlumpers BY NORMAN KLEIN DetroitAmericas back gate I Thousands of Europeans and Asiatics fbrbidden entry to the United States by our immigration laws are pouring into l the country through Detroit these days and have poured during the last eight years Detroit is the weak spot in the fron tier wall erected by Congress to shut out unwanted aliens At least Detroit Is one of the weak spots and along with Florida and the Mexican border is one of the principal points of entry for those wishing to crash the back gate In many a European village today the word has spread that if you cant come into the golden States with a quota visa the next best thing is to make a bee line for the Canadian bor der across from Detroit So many aliens have entered Detroit surreptitiously that Henry Ford has put a rule in force in"
